{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Extend paid paternity leave to 2 months",
        "additional_details": "As a father to a new born. 2 weeks is just NOT enough time to bond with your child. Newborns tale along time to get used to and get into a routine with them. This should be down to the mother. \r\n\r\nLike many of our wives and partners who have had to have a cesarean section, 2 weeks isn't an ideal length of time. \r\n\r\nWe need to be there for our wife just as much as the baby.\r\n\r\nPlease extend paternity leave.",
        "background": "Extend paternity leave from 2 weeks to 2 months. Fully paid by the employer.",
